-------------------------------------

1. NATIONAL STACK
Economy:
Stability:
Public Trust:
Infrastructure:
Defense:
Innovation:
Hidden Risk Trend:

2. PUBLIC SENTIMENT
Open Opinions:
Private Concerns:
